            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I'm not sure if my latest changes are any more readable than before... but I believe the `nil` check for `config.root_dir` is important, otherwise we are always checking for `node_modules`, even in a subdirectory (in other words, always checking if `vim.fs.joinpath((config or {}).root_dir, 'node_modules/.bin', cmd)` is executable).",
            "commit_id": "ec6dbf2f94d6489ee4240e0686d5d730a0ed9714",
